Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\pos(600,60)\fad(200,400)\bord0}终于要进行决赛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\pos(300,400)\fad(200,400)\bord0}我去比赛了 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背诵时间结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}なにわずに さくやこのはな ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}花开难波津 寒冬闭羞颜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央 取得五战全胜 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞 泽 高 中 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽原本没有呼口号的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是刚刚才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被这张「千早」给迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像平常那样 进攻就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たちわかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下因幡道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢了千早阵地裡的「たま」和「たち」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也是进攻歌牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须籐的S是「不停进攻」的S
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我领先了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须籐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是先拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都丢牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻吧 瑞泽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不确定也没关係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻敌阵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然激动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你原本就是这种性格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}まつとしきかば いまかへりこむ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}诸君劳久候 几欲再回还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かぜをいたみ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风急波浪涌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまはただ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至此劳空候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想进攻的 可是牌不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在自阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓攻击歌牌就是进攻敌阵 \N其中有给予对方精神打击的意味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也有送牌让自阵的配置变得更有利的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你可别被缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定每一张牌的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮晃晃的好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张「千早」好碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つくばねの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望筑波岭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易进攻敌阵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 都怪你不说抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢到了 抢到了 抢到一张了 继续加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 连我都在敌阵抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能输在进攻上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下一次一定要抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在个人战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张牌也就只是一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}こひぞつもりて ふちとなりぬる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}相思积岁月 早已化深潭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为队伍抢下一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}うかりける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神前空祷告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢到了 连续抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}绫{\fnHGHagoromoL\fs31\b0\fscx97\fscy103}瀬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 才不是连续抢到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才听到「う」就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还没有唸到「うか」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是抱著会手误的觉悟才出手的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来大家也要抢到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田 今天的读手有几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是高中的预赛 所以一直都是由那位女性担任的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这已经是第五场比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}はげしかれとは いのらぬものを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}初{\fnHGHagoromoL\fs31\b0\fscx97\fscy103}瀬{\r}山峰下 偏遭凛冽风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 那个读手的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的耳朵已经掌握到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おほえやま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山长平野阔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这次真的是连续抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早连续抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早开始进入状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道大家的心境开始变得轻鬆起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到的一张牌 不是普通的一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要连续抢到3张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算千早掌握了读手的习惯 但也不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也是刚好猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}まだふみもみず あまのはしだて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}渺杳无音信 几曾桥立游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 会在对方的心中留下烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あしびきの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野雉深山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会造成失误
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}注释：双重牌：当一方在敌阵拿到牌 而另一方手误时 得牌方可以送两张牌给失误方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 双重牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 须…须籐前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了中断不利的比赛走向而离席吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然俯视能让人冷静下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央 一张一张的夺下来噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ながながしよを ひとりかもねむ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}浸浸秋夜冷 只恐又独眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的反应确实很快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わたのはら こぎいでてみれば ひさかたの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茫茫船出海 放眼望天边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}歌牌可不仅仅于此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 被萌上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻入对方敌阵的围手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新也很擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的手掌也变得那么大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动牌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动这种地方？可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再东想西想了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那张牌对我来说很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管在何处都能抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像磁石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わすらるる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誓遭遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}しらつゆに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清秋原野上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みかきもり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫士焚篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早正压制著他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的差距是几张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13张 一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早追上了北央的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 绰号是肉包君什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是翠北歌牌会的西田同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你放弃歌牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为都没出席大赛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么强的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ひるはきえつつ ものをこそおもへ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}相思魂杳杳 长夜摧心肝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}このたびは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,币帛未曾带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘糟 那由太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在练习会上见到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这傢伙还只是初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然年长却比不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优征是个努力的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能到A级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为A级选手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也好久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あはぢしま
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡路来千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空牌？对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かくとだに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹艾草茂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为刚刚的能抢到的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚是我比较快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这样下去 我的小拇指在下面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 再这样 不是在我拇指的上面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知放弃啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那真的是我的牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这裡就算成自阵的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 别这样 听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}もゆるおもひを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}草木尽枯凋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みよしのの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故国秋风起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 翻身了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这傢伙怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲足过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 西田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふるさとさむく ころもうつなり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒砧催夜尽 户户捣衣衫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赢 我要以我的进攻歌牌来赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央胜两场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要胜一场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只要胜一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须籐前辈和甘糟前辈的情况都比预想的要棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救这局正是本人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么这傢伙那么难缠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百张中的「や」牌有4张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「やえ」和「やまざ」已经读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自阵右边的2张听到「や」就一起拍走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「よ」牌中「よのなか」的2张已经读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是「よも」和「よを」还没有读到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以「よ」出手要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ちぎりお」已经读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ちぎりき」和「ちは」听到「ち」就把2张拍走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「な」牌一共8张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ながら」「ながか」\N「なにし」「なつ」「なにわが」已经读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这裡就只剩「なげけ」和「なにはえ」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意空牌「なげき」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要上当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不像千早那样有过人的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不像西田那样能读懂比赛的走势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なげきつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叹息无閒暇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「なげき」还没读过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决胜字的变化我是绝对不会弄错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为大家的脊樑骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}いかにひさしき ものとかはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}迢迢怨遥夜 问君安可知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失误什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一次也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}よもすがら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜夜相思苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽胜一场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有6张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ねやのひまさへ つれなかりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}深闺门上缝 黯黯亦无情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比到胜负难分的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自阵的牌绝对不能在这时候被抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはえの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难波苇节短
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才是要防守自阵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}我的梦想也是成为名人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是比赛的顺境还是逆境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教会了我歌牌乐趣的正是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽胜两场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的 西田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想带持田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带大家去全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27}明明还有「ちぎりき」 竟然听到「ち」就去抢牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs27}你好厉害 好厉害 绫{\fnHGHagoromoL\fs24\b0\fscx97\fscy103}瀬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs27}她果然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs27}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下为什么她还能那样抢牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼神已经没有了想赢的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 你以前不发邮件的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去全国大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 新 他们是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来近江神宫看我们吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は过ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:52.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し风が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:58.09,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会话妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの场所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:19.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:25.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:31.04,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:40.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}梦の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走过回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:52.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微风轻轻吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:58.09,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}閒话家常也异常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依旧一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我们常常相约等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然记得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:19.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在我心怀强烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:25.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什么在目标之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:31.04,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在的话似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}试著伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:40.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在梦想的路上终有一天会再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}行くあてない街
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:34.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ひとり先を歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:39.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夕日に照らされた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}失いそうな心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:49.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}変わってゆくなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:54.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}想いもしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:22:00.01,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君と重ねた梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:05.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}いつの间に违う方へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:08.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}歩いてたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:14.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:19.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}远すぎる世界见つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:24.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ほら 响くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:31.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌 この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}向著无名的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:34.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}形单影隻地前进著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:39.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}被夕阳照得通红的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}近乎要遗失的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:49.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}却逐渐发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:54.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我万万也没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:22:00.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}与你在一起的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:05.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}不觉之间我们却已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:08.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}走向了不同的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:14.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻你我两人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:19.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著遥不可及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:24.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻 你瞧 歌声响彻
